<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='391000' id='t-391000'>I write a lot about &quot;security theater,&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='394000' id='t-394000'>which are products that make people feel secure,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='397000' id='t-397000'>but don't actually do anything.</span>
