<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='408000' id='t-408000'>So back to economics.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='410000' id='t-410000'>If economics, if the market, drives security,</span>
